  "text": "In cases of benign AN, insulin or an IGF have been suggested as promoters of enhanced epidermal cell propagation. Other mediators seem to be involved as well, including fibroblast growth factor (FGF) and tyrosine kinase receptors like the epidermal growth factor receptor [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
